Undid revision 898615067 by [[Special:Contributions/Tarl N.|Tarl N.]] ([[User talk:Tarl N.|talk]]) It is documentable that Author David Alexander was a contributor of investigative journalism to Penthouse Magazine (viz. Dave's Penthouse Papers, etc.) and as such has a legitimate right to inclusion. This editor has no personal connection to the cited author therefore the characterization of "self-promotion" is entirely without basis and the unwarranted deletion of the citation is vandalism.
